reviewText: I purchased this dvd set for the Winners Take All movie however Walking Tall and Boot Camp were a great addition.
my son loved winners take all. That's why I bought it. He liked the two other movies also.
i bought this for the movie 'winner takes all' .  its very hard to find , and i ended up with a couple other good movies too .
Winners Take All is one of my husband's favorite movies ever; so this is a great set at a good price. It's hard to find those nostalgic 80's movies anymore, so this is great :)
